data.text: @CharmaineTT @DebbieGarratt @aka_SPK_ No - I really don’t know what you think is BS. Here’s a fact. Among persons with whom I have a connection, in the last two years, 2 have died with covid. Average age 86. However 5 others have died suddenly. Average age ~50 (4 heart attacks & 1 brain haemorrhage). All were jabbed
@CharmaineTT @AlanJohnson1959 @aka_SPK_ What exactly are you saying is BS?
